控<br />\n妄顧公眾安全 人身權利<br />\n濫暴 濫用私刑 酷刑凌辱<br />\n<br />\n阻礙救援 違反國際人道法<br />\n封鎖現場多個小時 隔離救護員進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港正受人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n公然妨礙新聞自由 警方出公關稿籲媒體跟從<br />\n截斷交通 封鎖去道<br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span></span><br />\n實彈已出 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<br />\n召喚攬炒巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa153d8db67cccd6c4547812e352861704f1429","tid":1527073,"uid":98926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkvjRm4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkvjRm4.png&h=be721d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足聽日罷課罷工返課返工都好，可唔可以應承我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a>"},{"pid":"5f1084feedaaa95a57d87618f7e9e87b574671d2","tid":1527073,"uid":38533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740953d87c3384ccb5b7d02051e4c16bc8375c23","tid":1527073,"uid":124655,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"如果係即時就叫佢地行返轉頭散啦,<br />\n依家手足都係機場退緊出黎"},{"