},{"pid":"9c976ab5c12af3d4778c6556fc0e43714b4eb2fc","tid":1527073,"uid":100046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"大家要記住 你只係搭車/揸車進行每周末嘅機場交通壓力測試 諗目的先決定應該做啲咩<br />\n<br />\n唔駛慌嘅 揸車同搭車姐 <br />\n驚被圍困？點出入機場？傻啦，旅客搭咩出入 你咪搭咩出入 驚乜野？睇實旅客人數就得啦<br />\n<br />\n交通測試就唔要入客運大樓阻到旅客嘅，咁之但係你如果真係淆到驚被困機場，驚旅客有特別通道出入？ 咁咪上網買張full refund full fare Econ 排隊入terminal check in囉，再臨時決定都係唔飛，跟抵港旅客一齊離開囉<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">真係唔駛淆喎 手足</span></span>"},{"pid":"ffdc3bf8589e3330a2e8ab0c6877e28562eced6b","tid":1527073,"uid":164938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a697972ac3b3ee2353c7435a709a313b59b5f7c","tid":1527073,"uid":36162,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"做乜唔做功課先...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前話塞機場，我打開google map睇由馬灣計少要16-20km<br />\n21km即係半馬距離, 我咁屎要跑2:30, 有操開嘅一般兩鐘頭以內<br />\n行入去你預四個鐘已算快"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"可能入完去再出返黎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9972638fa38d28e129217bd316089f5ddfc38b","tid":1527073,"uid":55835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:07:25.000Z","msg":"成事萬人陪你行，驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56a864640cded0e7e804ec3c574f79003eec85a","tid":1527073,"uid":174191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:07:59.000Z","msg":"兩個月前邊會諗過可以徒步出入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef0029fc30a117f92a6775f65827dfbb4b634bc","tid":1527073,"uid":284932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"從青馬大橋步行去機場: 約 18.5 km (3 小時 50 分鐘)"},{"pid":"54e9d7b830361930d665a93b5e53b18e2b34a3c5","tid":1527073,"uid":233228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8f7fc9a7c00750a74a5dd69b2216c9e5ed377f7","tid":1527073,"uid