ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"依家唔停飛好似係因為擋唔住機場STAFF搭地鐵入東浦 再係逸東邨福逸樓巴士站入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4248af66b936e6272af869a6e47a44120f55ecc","tid":1527073,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74259653d96f820f01ed1b0a93b443c48cd6650a","tid":1527073,"uid":274329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>901 機場攻略</strong></span><br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou/832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou%2F832&d=I3kI68XCunzd%2BKkpJ1XxGGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=65999f5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou/832</a><br />\n<br />\n宣布啟動應變計劃 Plan C<br />\n東涌手足<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即刻行去機場</span></span></strong><br />\n有係機場行緊出黎嘅手足係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">半路等緊</span></span>大家<br />\n等東涌手足行埋入黎一齊會合再行去機場<br />\n諗返點解會話機場係春袋<br />\n係屋企嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">即刻去東涌</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注意散水撚！尊重前線決定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">未入到機場嘅，先喺東涌集合</span><br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要<span style=\"color: red;\">保護自己</span><br />\n- 利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=I3kI68XCunzd%2BKkpJ1XxGGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=f980934d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />